name: dYdX
public_notice: ethDYDX, a governance token for the dYdX v3 protocol, is undergoing a migration to dYdX Chain DYDX; currently, approximately 75% of all ethDYDX have been bridged to the dYdX Chain and converted into DYDX. If you have ethDYDX and want to convert your tokens into DYDX, read this how-to-bridge guide. For a detailed overview of the functionalities of dYdX Chain DYDX, read the dYdX Foundation’s Token Mechanics blog.
